    MSER
    MSER.java and Region.java are java ports of the C++ MSER implementation of MSER by Charles Dubout, charles.dubout@idiap.ch, downloaded from https://github.com/idiap/mser His C++ code is an implementation of "Linear Time Maximally Stable Extremal Regions", by D.
    MSEREdges
    class to explore the boundaries of the accumulated points in MSER regions to make edges that are complete contours (the level sets approach has a much larger pixel association than the few pixels of canny edges for example).
    MSEREdgesWrapper
    a convenience class to use MSEREdges.
    Region
